snippet.title: Amber Heard Hearts Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
'The Rum Diary' beauty Amber Heard stops by the Young Hollywood Studio for a "multifarious" chat about the film and sings the praises of director Bruce Robinson and co-star Johnny Depp. We also quiz the Austin native on homegrown topics like food trucks and line dancing, which somehow brings everything back full circle (i.e.: alcohol)! Hosted by Nikki Novak.
